Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,... Three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oui, Chef. Turn on the stove. Come on. Hurry up. Oui, Chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry! - Oui, Chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Alain? What did I say? What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Three distinct soils from three distinct local ecosystems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the Corporal asked for. That's what it's gotta look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her? I need more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ. Can't we just slip her some blinis?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the Foundling Guard to play marimba on your gonads, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep on like this. Dressing like a peasant dishing out slop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,whilst the goon squad does me a colonoscopy with their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Buck up, Malcolm. You might get fired by lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, yes, it's tingling. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can really feel that, actually. - It's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? It's not boiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:01:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have shit in your ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I said boiled and salted. Take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, take it back, your fancy French bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This crunchy one has got a bit of... zing to it, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I know I'm a broken record but are you sure it's safe to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be nutritious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very good for you. It's what we used to eat when we had nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but we don't have nothing now, do we? We, in fact, have quite a lot of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly your problem, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Your friend? I'm not your friend... - No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Nicky. We trust Herbert's folk remedies, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They cured us of the wretched mold, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go over more cuts later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The great culling of the fuckwit army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, on that point the staff is growing a bit jumpy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with the firings. Sorry. The contractions or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It... it's all a bit brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not hugely terrific for morale, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry, Nicky but we can't have dead weight on the payroll, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a lean operation. No baby fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And no leeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lenny, I have those financials for you to review. The "thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing. You know, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Belize fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, later. Later, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I have to make preparations for Daddy's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can handle the cabinet meeting by yourself, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- So are you going to tell me? - Tell you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you are dressed like an effete goatherder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've gone rural to please him, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Beg your pardon, certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to dodge the boot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go and show the Corporal your imported silk undies, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,eh, Mr. Ploughman? See how he fancies those.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You look exceedingly well, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be leading the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust the Chancellor is well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, glad to hear it, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we have a small gift for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bejeweled Frankish sword
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in the style of what historians believe the Foundling himself would've had...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your fucking sword. Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Vernham asked me to read you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Corporal Zubak and I have decided jointly on a package of reforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,one that is pursuant to our policy of improving the lives of working families.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Greed and foreign money must be stricken from our national character.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we shall introduce a new policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Large-scale transference of private property
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from the landowning elite to the working classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We must enact these broad reforms as soon as possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I say well done, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's land reform, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you'll know of the risks involved in land reform?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditionally, economic slowdown, food scarcity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have brushed up on your South African history?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I said we are doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll look into it once we have the Chancellor's go-ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you already have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just fucking read it to you. No, of course, of course. It just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just meant her official comp... compliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You will start planning it now because I told you to. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, of course. Certainly, sir. I'm... I'm sorry if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what happened to Emil Bartos, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir, but... - That was just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, Corporal. Thank you. We'll get started on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my friends all hail the Foundling's heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My loves from atop our proud mountain peaks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and over the fields of flowering sugar beets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we hear the song of our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They beckon to us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,calling us homeward to the values and traditions we once cherished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And in their simple joy and wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we discover the sacred and self-evident truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This beloved land must belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, very soon I will deliver
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,what previous Chancellor Edward Keplinger failed to deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A comprehensive program of land reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:09:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take back what the fiendish oligarchs stole from you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and eradicate rural poverty forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again shall your labor be forsaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again shall our dream be denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it. Was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect. Was it? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Perfect. - Wasn't too earnest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely, lovely, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We will need to discuss how we budget for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It could require dipping into the holding company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No... We keep all that separate. Thank you, Mr. Singer. Herbert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fucking great, right? Just like in our dream, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! No, yes. No, exactly like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Land reform. Chunky words. Exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll spare a thought for the Americans. They'll be in fucking fits over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Elena. We don't think about them anymore, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They are gone now. It's just us and our people right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No, of course. Only being puckish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here you are, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They brought your tea. Shall I pour us some?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking, Lenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It... it really punches through, land reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the... the Robin Hood of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You do see the problem, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"The problem"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be Robin Hood and the king at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The holding company, Lenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Both? No, you can't give the country back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,while continuing to stash half of it in your purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We skim a little cream off the top. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than a little cream, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely she doesn't mean "reform"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in the most literal sense of changing the form of what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't care what she means.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She would bankrupt this country if that belligerent buffalo tells her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan was always to elevate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Elevate him, yes. Not turn him into Herbert the fucking Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of him that our cobalt mines lie dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of him, our GDP is shrinking like a sphincter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He has made the American cash cow leave for greener pastures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll lose interest. She always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What if this time, she doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, as per your request, I've compiled a full report
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,on recent American media trends and intelligence chatter. And the dominant conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of course continues to be Taiwan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with tensions escalating
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the US State Department's attempting to engage China...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, let's start with Europe, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes. Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've seen increased focus on Germany's troubled markets...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Closer to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Closer than Germany, Madam. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the US continues to eye opportunities for investment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Faban Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, our assets in the region are monitoring...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing on us, no? No fun crackle on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god. Kansas frump?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what's her name? Holt. Senator Holt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Madam, I would say the new isolationist policies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,devised by Corporal Zubak and yourself appear to have succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your government figure minimally in American media of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems as though that they've moved on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is what you wanted, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy almost birthday, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ, look at you. Painted up like a Dutch whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. These are dead. You're dead. Lots in common. Much to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've gone very rural here. You're going to hate it. Well, tough tits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop looking at me like that. I'm... I'm fine. I'm better than fine, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... Well, I haven't been sleeping well, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it happens to be a terrific idea, land reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not weak or boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And just because it isn't big enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your Faban annexation pipe dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Delusional.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real world, Daddy. Grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're wrong about Herbert, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully in control of that situation. Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's a real man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a dried-up old cricket with teensy little balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're jealous? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you're trying to drive me mad, like Mommy? Well, it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am father-inoculated. I... I spit you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse you. I reject you because you are fucking pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I'm sorry. Sorry. No, sorry. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just forget about it, shall we, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't want to spoil your big day tomorrow, all right? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm up, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! All right. God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoulders back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, from the hips, from the hips. Here. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'm just a bit tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to Daddy earlier and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I just was thinking, is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is it right, land reform? Is it what we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it is. It... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right. I think it is, yes. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the rope going slack, that's all. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... do think it will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I... I do like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what are you doing? God, what...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come here. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here. Get on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on, get down! Next to the vent! - My hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're hurting me! - Closer to the vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- No... - Come on, no. Right next to it. - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- No! - Right next to it! Come on, breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on, breathe your fuckin' poison! - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on! - No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. I can't do it. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Elena, you cannot do it because you are not cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still sick in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not inside these walls. It's inside you. Let it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- What? - Really let it out. Tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you hiding? Tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god. Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, fuck me. I don't know. Where would I begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's everywhere. There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Slush funds in Belize State Bank, the holding company.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fucking a billion or more in assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My name, Nicky's name, through our partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands, thousands of fucking strings of... of money
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,purloined from local businesses, farms, pension funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... just shit I can't ever unravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... I have made such a fucking mess. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Poetry has always been the lifeblood of any thriving civil society
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and with the blessed help of our government
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,these poetry centers shall be the fountains
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from which our national spirit might quaff if I may say, poetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck happened? She's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, Elena, what happened? - Oh, thank you, child. Look, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous. We were exercising, and I overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unacceptable, Corporal. You can't push her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't been eating well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been eating well for the first time in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm fine. I just slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that gym floor, Nicky. It's like a fucking dolphin's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Fetch Agnes. We're getting the Chancellor a proper dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, you're not. - Now listen, Corporal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been very patient with your process these past few months
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and I believe we've accommodated each other
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with as little friction as can be expected under the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But now my wife's health and happiness have been jeopardized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. She's happy, and she's healthy. The only one who is not is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If my energy is low it's because I'm not sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sleeping? You're a house cat on opium, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not sleeping well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. It's your twitching, Nicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your hypnic jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how can I sleep with all that foot jiggling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's just... Well, we had a little chat and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps you and I ought to try a night apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to regulate, Nicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Is this just for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Just for tonight. Just a night. Or a... few.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- And this is your idea or his idea? - It's our idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Herbert's suggestion which I agree with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, Madam. How can I help? Hello, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You would like to know how you can help?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Corporal, if you please. Yes, I do please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I please to fuckin' hang you out that window by your ankles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that's your concern, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Elena nearly died sliding on that ice rink you call a gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Herbert, please, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Corporal, I can assure you that the gymnasium
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and indeed every inch of this Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,has been maintained to the standard to which it's always been maintained
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,which is to say, the very highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You harm her again we send you to the zoo as lion food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Corporal. Think we understand each other quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god. Out! Everyone, please. I just... I'm getting an early night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone, eyes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes up. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam and Corporal Zubak have asked that the menu for Joseph's birthday dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,include "folk cuisine of thorough and rigorous nutrition."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My condolences to your whisks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Three more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, more. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost out of Oskar's pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter, I need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I deviate from the new medical regime
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll have me in prison by suppertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry. - Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And there we are. Or more like this probably?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:23:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, right. Right a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- No? No, no. Right... Or left? Oh, no... - Oh, stop it, oh, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Only joking. - Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your wrist still hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.19,0:24:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friend Diazepam might do you good. Ease the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Nicky. Herbert's given me a tincture thingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's working, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.72,0:24:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.45,0:24:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And who the fuck are all these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.33,0:25:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it had to be a birthday party with real people
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.21,0:25:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,not some fancy fucks and fine China
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so I took the liberty of inviting some of our people from the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.88,0:25:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.05,0:25:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.05,0:25:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you know, to... to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.06,0:25:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.43,0:25:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What you told me about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.23,0:25:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell... tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.36,0:25:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you don't have to tell details.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.40,0:25:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You just tell them you made mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.49,0:25:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that you took from them, and clean your conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.24,0:25:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.07,0:25:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- No. I don't think  I'll be doing that. - Why not? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.33,0:25:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... D'you... It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.99,0:25:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,D'you know it's not really that sort of occasion, hm? Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.62,0:25:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's... it's just more of a celebration. Yes, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.34,0:25:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Elena... - Let's sit down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.05,0:26:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. I'm so thrilled you are all here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.56,0:26:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are the real people
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.69,0:26:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what my father would've wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.23,0:26:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As for you, birthday boy 83 today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.66,0:26:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.49,0:26:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you and I both know that you are still very much here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And so happy birthday to Daddy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.92,0:26:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Many more
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.88,0:26:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bless you all for joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.22,0:26:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.72,0:26:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really good at speeches, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.90,0:26:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,my people had a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.94,0:26:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"You may build it as tall as you want
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.45,0:27:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but you build it from our earth!"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.70,0:27:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Our earth! - Our earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.29,0:27:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our earth, yes! And I would like to add...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.88,0:27:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We would like to add
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.96,0:27:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we are terribly sorry for everything that has been taken away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.42,0:27:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your toil, your hope, your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.56,0:28:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.94,0:28:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen, I know I said some things yesterday that weren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.19,0:28:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't very kind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.78,0:28:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.78,0:28:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- I just want... - Shut your fucking mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.45,0:28:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry, I... - And stop apologizing, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.33,0:28:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wi... I wi... I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.46,0:28:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,These hogs may call you Chancellor but I know who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.22,0:28:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A vapid, feckless, political whore with no principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.69,0:28:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A comic figure bereft of vision easily ruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.53,0:29:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All tits and no spine. Like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.16,0:29:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes, I... I kn... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.28,0:29:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god. Can't you speak properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.66,0:29:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't... Stop saying that. I... I'm trying, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.46,0:29:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You always just lie back and take it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.21,0:29:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Americans loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.05,0:29:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to take it from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.09,0:29:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He has you sucking his cock doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.56,0:29:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer, you ugly bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.90,0:29:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.19,0:29:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.40,0:29:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Be bold for once
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.28,0:29:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in your hollow little life. Seize the mantle of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.74,0:29:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes, I'll try. I'll try, promise. Promise, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.82,0:30:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having a land reform planning meeting after this
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.78,0:30:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so I will fill you in on everything later, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.86,0:30:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll join the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.12,0:30:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Agnes? Would you ask Mr. Laskin to let them know, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.79,0:30:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, Ma'am. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.46,0:30:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here we go. Strap in, my fuckaneers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.01,0:30:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I think I've come around, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.34,0:30:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.09,0:30:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think perhaps this might be a marvelous notion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.14,0:30:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure. Redistribute property. Tank the economy. Empty the grocers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.14,0:31:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,White Zimbabwe, here we come.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.19,0:31:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if one had a summer cottage at Lake Ober somethin' like that wouldn't be,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.61,0:31:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,as it were "redistributed," would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.91,0:31:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Chancellor, Corporal Zubak so glad you could both join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.91,0:31:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. We have prepared for you both
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.00,0:31:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a planning precis regarding the rollout of what we'd like to call
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.88,0:31:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the Vernham Agrarian Reform and Development Program.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.59,0:31:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you'd like to take a glance
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.18,0:31:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,at the land reform planning packets in front of you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.60,0:31:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we thought we'd might like to start with, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.14,0:31:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Section One. Farm Expropriation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.06,0:31:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this has been adjusted to our current budget...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.23,0:31:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister Singer that's not where I'd like to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.11,0:31:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, very well, Madam. Where would you like to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.40,0:31:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The land itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.32,0:31:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, in so far as?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.53,0:31:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Securing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.54,0:31:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Securing it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.16,0:32:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, one needs to secure the land before reforming it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, certainly, Madam and in terms of the actionable...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.63,0:32:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Priority one is to protect the security and autonomy of our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.85,0:32:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And a program of reunification with our Faban brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.81,0:32:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only way to ensure our sovereignty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.44,0:32:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Reunification?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.82,0:32:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this might get some chatter
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.45,0:32:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from our American friends, don't you think, Mr. Laskin?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.24,0:32:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, I hope my report, my counsel, did not animate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.33,0:32:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.58,0:32:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I imagine your job is about to become quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.13,0:32:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are we... - Still our plan, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.63,0:32:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking back what's been stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.43,0:32:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which would be impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.05,0:32:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,without reuniting with the Faban Corridor first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.31,0:33:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.10,0:33:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. It's cleaner this way. And it's actually the only way. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.61,0:33:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, if you are indeed proposing an annexation of the Faban Corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.49,0:33:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I must ardently advise extreme caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.49,0:33:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, no contingency plans exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.54,0:33:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We would be playing the invasion by ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.83,0:33:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows how the NATO powers will react
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.08,0:33:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and if the security forces in the Faban zone resist
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.25,0:33:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be a bloodbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.67,0:33:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Laskin no one is proposing an invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.89,0:33:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.85,0:33:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an expression of peace and love towards our countrymen across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.89,0:33:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- But, Madam... - Onwards, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.02,0:33:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's aim to mobilize by... end of the week?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.07,0:33:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that sounds reasonable, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.23,0:33:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Herbert we should send you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.95,0:33:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give you a new title. Something like... "Faban Freedom Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.82,0:34:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that. Something fun. Snappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.45,0:34:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.46,0:34:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My loves at long last, we have arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.76,0:34:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at the sacred hour of our glorious dream realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.93,0:34:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it appears a reckoning has finally arrived for all
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.05,0:34:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,who ever desired Faban
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.80,0:34:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,self-determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.77,0:34:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have dispatched top aides
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.23,0:34:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,including newly appointed Faban Freedom Commander Herbert Zubak
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.52,0:34:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to ensure that these ancestral lands are reclaimed with the utmost care.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.07,0:34:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Vernham and her supporters
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.36,0:34:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,have vied for these 800 square miles
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.78,0:34:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of ethnic mountain land for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.41,0:34:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Vernham's regime has been careful to describe
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.29,0:34:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the operation as a "lawful annexation."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.58,0:34:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Vernham's defiant turnabout...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.33,0:34:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the shots we're seeing unmarked vehicles moving silently into Faban territory
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.55,0:34:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,are impossible to deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.59,0:34:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all the hallmarks of an occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.72,0:35:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't an occupation, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.10,0:35:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as I speak, the Faban Parliament is voting unanimously to approve this reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.43,0:35:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A mere 12 days after Vernham entered the Faban Corridor illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.02,0:35:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sources say Faban legislators
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.15,0:35:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,have been forced at gunpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.23,0:35:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to unanimously approve annexation making it official.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.20,0:35:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The White House responded swiftly today calling the invasion
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.82,0:35:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"a tragic assault on Faban self-determination
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.29,0:35:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and a mockery of NATO peacekeeping efforts."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.66,0:35:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The developments in the Faban Corridor this week
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.83,0:35:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,underscore the importance of our transatlantic partnerships.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.29,0:35:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Vernham calls this a reunification
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.88,0:35:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but we know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.84,0:35:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She seized this land illegally
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.68,0:35:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and there will be consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.39,0:35:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Vernham's long-held dream of regaining control of the Faban Corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.40,0:35:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,has finally been realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.86,0:35:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Most would agree that a reunion with our Faban brothers and sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.24,0:36:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is a cause for celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But what will be the long-term effects on our...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.88,0:36:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.06,0:36:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you all. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.35,0:36:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Chancellor, does last week's military operation in the Faban...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.10,0:36:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Military operation"? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.31,0:36:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not use these words, "military operation."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.07,0:36:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not a single shot has been fired in the Faban Corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.53,0:36:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and there have been no casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.36,0:36:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Chancellor, to what extent does this reunion violate international agreements?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.95,0:36:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The agreements to which you refer are archaic and, therefore, not legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.71,0:36:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All we are doing is realizing our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.30,0:37:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dream of a new Europe without limits, without cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.84,0:37:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I assure you our actions are in full compliance with the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.22,0:37:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who's next? - Madam Chancellor?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.81,0:37:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.77,0:37:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you thought through all the possible risks?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.69,0:37:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Economic sanctions, a possible visa ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.19,0:37:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask the United States if they thought through the possible risks of their exploits
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.69,0:37:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in Afghanistan, Iraq Yemen, Libya, Indonesia, Central America
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.07,0:37:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,every corner of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.87,0:37:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Actions which were carried out at great human cost
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.53,0:37:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with no resulting UN sanctions whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.12,0:37:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask them about that, did you? No, I didn't think you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.83,0:37:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Madam, the stock market - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.33,0:37:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,has declined sharply and exchange rates have hit record lows. Yeah, money likes quiet, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.34,0:37:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, there is noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our erstwhile friends across the Atlantic are responsible for that noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.64,0:37:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But once they settle down, the markets will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.01,0:37:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, but... - Yeah, this is no longer a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.06,0:37:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me finish. Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.43,0:37:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there are times when one must choose the hardest road.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.48,0:38:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have chosen that road and I have done so
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.99,0:38:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of liberty. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.74,0:38:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.13,0:38:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What have we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.88,0:38:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I present you a cornerstone of the Monastery of the Holy Trinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.26,0:38:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ancient spiritual home of our brothers in the Faban lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.60,0:38:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple peasants once fought to get this relic back
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.81,0:38:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from the land that it leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.35,0:38:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in our dream, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.11,0:38:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's... that's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.16,0:38:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Elena, as soon as we can we should start on the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.66,0:38:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"The rest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.12,0:38:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of our dream. Land reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.96,0:39:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Oh, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah, of course. No, we must give land reform the best chance of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.01,0:39:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- When? - When the Faban turbulence is behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.35,0:39:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our budget has shifted now
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.76,0:39:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and significant aid will need to be sent to the Faban Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.27,0:39:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rest of our funds, we ought to set aside in case of any repercussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.81,0:39:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when will our dream come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.48,0:39:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.90,0:39:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The remainder of which we'll budget for next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.74,0:39:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the year after. Year after?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.74,0:39:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to be careless, Herbert. Land reform is simply too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.97,0:39:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloody hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.43,0:39:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.85,0:40:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been instructed to bring you this. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.86,0:40:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the clothes she wants you to wear for the banquet tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.57,0:40:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that lovely for the Faban victory party. I'm not wearing this Nutcracker shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.49,0:40:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She requested that you do, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.87,0:40:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.09,0:40:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.02,0:40:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I've got some spare undershirts in there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.61,0:40:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being nice to me? It's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.77,0:40:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm just doin' me job, my stupid job.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.91,0:40:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hail the conquering hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.66,0:40:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.33,0:41:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.88,0:41:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire Western world is about to pig fuck us with sanctions
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.00,0:41:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.67,0:41:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, look, I say you're stressed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.97,0:41:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but you must admit, our plan to sideline the Corporal has worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.34,0:41:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan, sir, was to get back to business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.22,0:41:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is emphatically not business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.73,0:41:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose my head knows that's true
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.98,0:41:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,yet I must confess, my heart feels oddly tickled.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.19,0:41:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find the imminent demise of our economy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.95,0:41:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly outweighs the benefits to your love life, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.41,0:41:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think we could ride out those sanctions somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.25,0:41:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with our new plan C?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.21,0:41:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. China.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.25,0:41:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A cold, heartless superpower that's going to sort out all our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.21,0:41:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Think happy thoughts, Laskin. It's time to twist the night away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.49,0:42:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the outfit, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.58,0:42:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember, if you're feeling unwell
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.46,0:42:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,just come and find me, all right? Come and find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.22,0:42:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.56,0:42:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, did you write a speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.12,0:43:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing here? Cheers, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.19,0:43:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.66,0:43:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.78,0:43:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and welcome, welcome one and all to the Heroes' Banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.79,0:43:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we celebrate our returning heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.29,0:43:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and our joyous reunification with our Faban brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.59,0:44:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the question is are you ready to party?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.06,0:44:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.10,0:44:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd keep an eye on that Bordeaux by the way, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.39,0:44:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,NATO might snatch that back by the intermission.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.73,0:44:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And haven't you all scrubbed up well? Don't ya all look great?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.40,0:44:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we have down here? It's Emil Bartos
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.28,0:44:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and he seems to be chaperoning his granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.29,0:44:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And how old is she, if I may inquire?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.08,0:44:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like she'd be just as happy with a ice cream and a pony ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.25,0:44:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's imagine how poor, dear, old Keplinger is feeling right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.05,0:44:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know he's gonna be watchin' this, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.47,0:44:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know he's watching this up there in his mansion in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.77,0:44:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,weeping into his chardonnay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.23,0:44:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Former Chancellor of course you hate reunification.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.15,0:45:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew that after your first two divorces.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.78,0:45:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But, my friends, let's consider for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.49,0:45:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,what's happening in this very country outside these four walls now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.04,0:45:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A pointless, needless, wasteful, expensive undertaking
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.21,0:45:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that's gonna drag on for years and years and years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.09,0:45:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking, of course about the national poetry centers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.51,0:45:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, oh, dear. Mr. Vernham's not looking happy with that one. Mr. Vernham's not looking happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.68,0:45:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now, that was rather tame. Come on. - If you don't like the material
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.81,0:45:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you could write a poem about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.64,0:45:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Chancellor? Mr. Bartos would like to discuss the China brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.98,0:45:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,La... later.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.11,0:45:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Paging Dr. Freud. Chancellor's husband. It's very clear who wears the trousers...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.78,0:45:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck is the China brief?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.49,0:45:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine it's where China is discussed briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.12,0:46:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a cheer if you're Special Forces! The Air Force! The Security Service!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.96,0:46:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Nicholas, I have a submission for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.80,0:46:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're still taking submissions... Go for it! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.26,0:46:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...but my literary assistant will bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.56,0:46:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.81,0:46:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.98,0:46:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"There once was a man so astounding
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.56,0:46:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,whose job was so very confounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.15,0:46:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He lived at the Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.94,0:46:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and tugged on his phallus
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.36,0:46:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and shouted 'My granddad's the Foundling!'"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.37,0:47:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oskar! All right. It's okay. Deep breaths. Deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.25,0:47:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fuck off. - I'm trying to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.67,0:47:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You had your chance to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.21,0:47:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right. Mom's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.88,0:47:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a scoff. It's a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.43,0:47:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All a big joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.43,0:47:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.90,0:47:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget tomorrow. The bankers, the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.94,0:47:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.32,0:47:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- See you tomorrow. - See you tomorrow. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.45,0:47:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.62,0:47:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was patchy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.08,0:48:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Comedy is like that. Absolutely no one's good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.09,0:48:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.68,0:48:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you tired? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.48,0:48:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bit cranky?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.65,0:48:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.86,0:48:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- You sure? - Yes, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.20,0:48:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure I believe you, but... Whatever. Long night.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.75,0:48:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? Have you always done that? Done what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.09,0:48:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- That sniff. You do a sniff now. - A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.38,0:48:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.26,0:48:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.93,0:48:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not aware of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.89,0:49:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.77,0:49:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not be aware of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.35,0:49:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.48,0:49:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not aware there's something you do many times a day
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.19,0:49:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that you never used to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.57,0:49:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I do a sniff, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.57,0:49:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do. I just told you that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.28,0:49:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.79,0:49:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No, doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.00,0:49:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a bit irritating that you won't acknowledge that you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.17,0:49:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you find me irritating? No, that's not what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.67,0:49:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's how you seem with me. It's how I seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.92,0:49:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is it? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.51,0:49:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.93,0:49:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was barely aware of you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.73,0:49:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.44,0:49:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was celebrating my country and our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.45,0:49:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Must my attention always be on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.74,0:50:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you meeting with Bartos?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.29,0:50:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.37,0:50:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.13,0:50:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you meeting with Bartos?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.38,0:50:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's free to practice business
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.51,0:50:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and his business is of consequence to my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.68,0:50:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this man is of no consequence to us. None whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.85,0:50:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, just a check-in. Check-in on what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.48,0:50:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff. Few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.06,0:50:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,China?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.69,0:50:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, perhaps, an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.82,0:50:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A free-trade deal with the largest nation on Earth who oppose our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.07,0:50:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... is that a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.45,0:50:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"You may build it as tall as you like but you build it from our earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.37,0:50:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.88,0:50:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That something your mommy would sing in the beet fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.21,0:51:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Elena. Look at me. It's our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.76,0:51:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.18,0:51:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- What? - Your dream, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.98,0:51:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't fucking dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.73,0:51:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god, is that so shocking?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.90,0:51:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ. Fucking grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.16,0:51:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I occasionally dream but I don't remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.49,0:51:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.37,0:51:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do. Your dreams come from the mind of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.01,0:51:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not enormously bright, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.26,0:51:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.10,0:51:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Big baby ox man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.85,0:51:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father always knew that you are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.57,0:51:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor baby ox.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.03,0:52:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You steal money from poor people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.07,0:52:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you hide it and you turn your soul to shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.49,0:52:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you dream about fucking me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.50,0:52:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.29,0:52:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You dream about fucking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.63,0:52:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't dream about fucking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.27,0:52:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were fun. You used to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.56,0:52:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're boring now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.69,0:52:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.28,0:52:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.53,0:52:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That you dream about fucking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.21,0:52:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you do not have a graceful mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.67,0:52:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep sputtering, ox.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.05,0:53:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me fucking ox!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.43,0:53:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an ox, you hear me? Look at me. I'm not a fucking ox!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.14,0:53:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're a butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.61,0:53:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.83,0:54:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.66,0:54:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing I'd like to speak with you about, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.71,0:54:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.71,0:55:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The folk remedies prescribed by the former Chief of Health and Safety
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.88,0:55:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,have not been working
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.22,0:55:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and Oskar has been having seizures again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.93,0:55:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Agnes! Why was I not told?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.77,0:55:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I mean, I wanted to be honest with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.27,0:55:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad you're honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.69,0:55:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother to mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.70,0:55:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course. We must resume Oskar's prior treatment immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.62,0:55:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... That means... I can't tell you how much that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.95,0:55:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.00,0:55:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,co-parenting is about honesty
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.96,0:55:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and for you to have withheld information about Oskar's condition
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.54,0:55:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,well, it doesn't make me feel like we're operating in good faith, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.55,0:55:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think, the best thing for Oskar
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.76,0:55:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,would be for him to stay here with me so I can supervise his treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.48,0:56:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I... I really can't trust you right now, Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.52,0:56:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so disappointing. I'm sure you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.86,0:56:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.23,0:56:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you. - I...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.78,0:56:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
